OL,3,CEstimated cost of Belfast's Grand
OL,4,CCentral Station rises to #340m
OL,6,FThe estimated cost of a major new
OL,7,Ftransport hub in Belfast has risen to
OL,8,F#340 million, it has emerged.
OL,10,FGrand Central Station in Belfast is
OL,11,Fset to become the largest integrated
OL,12,Ftransport hub in Ireland and will
OL,13,Freplace the current bus and rail
OL,14,Ffacilities at Europa Bus Centre and
OL,15,FGreat Victoria Street train station.
OL,17,FIt will also house the Enterprise
OL,18,Ftrain service to Dublin.
