OL,3,CEstimated cost of Belfast's Grand
OL,4,CCentral Station rises to #340m
OL,6,FStormont Infrastructure Minister John
OL,7,FO'Dowd told MLAs the project is
OL,8,F"progressing well" with the first
OL,9,Fphase due to be operational by autumn,
OL,10,Fand the full station and associated
OL,11,Fpublic realm works due to be completed
OL,12,Fby the end of 2025.
OL,14,FDUP MLA Jonathan Buckley asked the
OL,15,Fminister about the latest cost of the
OL,16,Fproject during Assembly questions for
OL,17,Fhis department on Tuesday.
OL,19,FGrand Central Station had previously
OL,20,Fbeen described as a #200 million
OL,21,Fproject.
