OL,3,CEstimated cost of Belfast's Grand
OL,4,CCentral Station rises to #340m
OL,6,FMr O'Dowd said the total cost had been
OL,7,Fprojected to be #295 million when the
OL,8,Ffull business case was approved in
OL,9,FNovember 2020.
OL,11,F"The latest cost estimate is #340
OL,12,Fmillion which is #45 million higher
OL,13,Fthan the estimated cost," he said.
OL,15,F"The vast majority of this cost
OL,16,Fincrease is due to extraordinary
OL,17,Finflation that has impacted on all
OL,18,Fmajor capital projects.
