OL,6,F"The project is due to be completed by
OL,7,Fquarter four 2025 which is in line
OL,8,Fwith the date indicated in the
OL,9,Fapproved full business case."
OL,11,FThe full site will include 1.3 million
OL,12,Fsquare feet of office, residential,
OL,13,Fstudent housing, retail and leisure
OL,14,Fspace, as well as Saltwater Square, a
OL,15,Fnew public realm space for outdoor
OL,16,Fperformances and community events.
