OL,6,FEarlier this month, Belfast city
OL,7,Fcouncillors voted for dual Irish and
OL,8,FEnglish language signage to be
OL,9,Finstalled at the land it has
OL,10,Fresponsibility for around the new
OL,11,Fstation and surrounding Weaver's Cross
OL,12,Farea.
OL,14,FMr O'Dowd was asked by People Before
OL,15,FProfit MLA Gerry Carroll if he could
OL,16,Fcommit to issuing a directive to
OL,17,FTranslink to implement dual language
OL,18,Fsignage at all transport centres
OL,19,Fincluding Grand Central.
