OL,6,FThe minister said his understanding is
OL,7,Fthat he does not have the authority to
OL,8,Fissue such a directive.
OL,10,F"But I have, and my officials have
OL,11,Fbeen engaging with Translink in
OL,12,Frelation to this matter," he said.
OL,14,F"I think there is an opportunity here
OL,15,Ffor this state of the art station to
OL,16,Fhave all of the languages which
OL,17,Frepresent the communities which it
OL,18,Fserves, and I have encouraged
OL,19,FTranslink to do that," he said.
OL,21,F"But it is a decision for Translink.
